====Usage notes====
Often used interchangeably in compounds with {{l|ja|器|tr=[[き]], ''[[ki]]''}} to indicate “machine”, with the distinction that 機 implies a larger machine, such as an airplane, while 器 implies a smaller device, possibly hand-held. Compare {{l|ja|飛行機|tr=''hikōki''|gloss=airplane}} with {{l|ja|食器|''shokki''|gloss=tableware}}.

