=====Idioms=====
* {{l|ja|機が熟する|tr=[[きがじゅくする]], ''[[ki ga juku suru]]''}}: the [[time is ripe]]; a [[golden opportunity]]
* {{l|ja|機に乗じる|tr=[[きにじょうじる]], ''[[ki ni jōjiru]]''}}, {{l|ja|機に投じる|tr=[[きにとうじる]], ''[[ki ni tōjiru]]''}}: to [[sieze the moment]], to [[jump at the chance]]
